<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00BFFF 0%, #0099CC 100%); min-height: 60vh;" class="text-white d-flex align-items-center">
  <div class="container text-center py-5">
    <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold" style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); letter-spacing: 2px;">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-baseball-bat-ball"></i> Ballpark Note
    </h1>
    <p class="fs-3 fw-semibold mt-3" style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
      野球観戦の思い出を、記録しよう。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <p class="fs-5">ようこそ！<%= current_user.email %>さん</p>
        <%= link_to "観戦記録を見る →", games_path, class: "btn btn-light btn-lg fw-bold me-3 px-4", style: "color: #0099CC;" %>
        <%= link_to "ログアウト", destroy_user_session_path, data: { turbo_method: :delete }, class: "btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-light btn-lg fw-bold me-3 px-4", style: "color: #0099CC;" %>
        <%= link_to "新規登録 →", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn fw-bold btn-lg px-4", style: "background: #FF4500; color: white; border: none;" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
  <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4" style="color: #0099CC;">Ballpark Noteでできること</h2>
  <div class="row g-4 text-center">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
        <div class="card-body py-4">
          <div class="fs-1 mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-baseball"></i></div>
          <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">野球観戦の思い出を記録</h5>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">後から見返して懐かしめる</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
        <div class="card-body py-4">
          <div class="fs-1 mb-3"><i class="fa-brands fa-untappd"></i></div>
          <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">お酒の数も記録</h5>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">球場ではお酒を飲むのも醍醐味の一つ</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
        <div class="card-body py-4">
          <div class="fs-1 mb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-pen"></i></div>
          <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">自分だけの野球日記</h5>
          <p class="card-text text-muted">メモ機能で試合の感想を書き残しちゃおう</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>